Advanced Skin Treatments

We pride our selves on being skin experts,

This means offering advanced skin treatments.

Microneedling

Microneedling is often referred to as collagen induction therapy because the needles delivered into the skin stimulate the body’s collagen production. Collagen is a protein that supports the underlying dermal structure to produce skin that is soft and smooth.

Data Collection

Creating data pipelines for collection and cleaning of the data based on the ML needs

AI/ML Solution

Training and Validating custom ML models that best suits the needs and the data

Solution Roadmap

Helping to better understand the needs for serving the ML solution within the organization or the product (PoC MVP)

Production Ready ML

Making the ML solution production ready based on the needs of the client (Embedded, self hosted, AWS, Azure, etc.)

Packaging and Scaling

Help the client create dynamic solutions and services around the ML solution using modern technologies (React, Rest APIs, and etc.)

ML Solution monitoring

Help the client monitor the ML solution over time

ML Maintenance Roadmap

Action plan to keep the ML models up-to-date based on the newly collected data

Platform Maintenance Roadmap

Maintenance plan and roadmap for the whole solution
